OL,3,CHospital trust issues warning as
OL,4,Cemergency department faces high demand
OL,6,FThere are more than 100 patients in
OL,7,Fthe Trust's hospitals who have flu or
OL,8,Fanother respiratory condition.
OL,10,FPeople heading to A&E are being urged,
OL,11,Fif possible, to wait alone to reduce
OL,12,Fnumbers in the waiting area.
OL,14,FThe Trust is asking people to consider
OL,15,Falternative services if their
OL,16,Fcondition is not life or limb
OL,17,Fthreatening.
