OL,3,CHospital trust issues warning as
OL,4,Cemergency department faces high demand
OL,6,FAnyone with symptoms of flu, Covid,
OL,7,Fvomiting or diarrhoea are also being
OL,8,Fasked to not visit patients, in order
OL,9,Fto keep them safe.
OL,11,FPaul Grundy, chief medical officer at
OL,12,FUniversity Hospital Southampton, said:
OL,13,F"The hospital is currently extremely
OL,14,Fbusy with over 400 patients attending
OL,15,Fthe emergency department (ED) daily
OL,16,Fand the high prevalence of flu and
OL,17,Fother respiratory illnesses is
OL,18,Fsignificantly impacting our bed
OL,19,Favailability.
