OL,3,CHospital trust issues warning as
OL,4,Cemergency department faces high demand
OL,6,F"We ask the public to consider three
OL,7,Fthings: only come to the ED for life
OL,8,For limb-threatening illnesses; if
OL,9,Fvisiting loved ones in the hospital,
OL,10,Fplease avoid coming if you are unwell,
OL,11,Fespecially with flu-like symptoms,
OL,12,FCOVID, or diarrhoea and vomiting as
OL,13,Fthese can harm vulnerable patients;
OL,14,Fand if you have a loved one awaiting
OL,15,Fdischarge, please help us in ensuring
OL,16,Fa timely discharge. Thank you for your
OL,17,Fongoing support."
